node.text: What Pickett lacks in height, he makes up for in personality. Would you choose a Bowtruckle as a pocket-sized companion?

node.accessibility_caption: A finely crafted sculpture of a Bowtruckle; the green, twig-like magical beast.

node.text: @onni_crafts's finely forged magical creatures would be right at home in Newt's suitcase. Which sculpture is your favourite? #CreatorOfTheMonth #FantasticFans

node.text: Even when she's on the job, Vinda Rosier flaunts formidable fashion. Tag a friend whose work wardrobe is as stylish as hers.
